name: Mu-Chan
description: I am Mu, the third member of Riko Wako(Doge-Kabosu mama) family, owner of Neiro and Cocoro. In my house they call me Mu-chan. I was adopted ,and now I am eternally grateful for the part she played in bringing me in a family ❤️ The community has now formed to celebrate the arrival of this new dog to the family alongside Neiro and Cocoro! Upon arriving to the family Mu also attended the first anniversary of Kabosu-Chan.
